    "en": {
      "title": "The Essential Public Services Bill will be approved by the House next Wednesday",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "The Essential Public Service Bill is scheduled to be passed in the Parliament next (6) Wednesday.",
        "The Parliamentary Communications Division says that this bill is to be passed without debate.",
        "The purpose of this bill is to make necessary provisions for efficient delivery of essential public services."
